.
APDISTI2DEF  INIT             "1-8,31-38,9-16,23-30,40-46,171-173"    (Index definitions for Key 2)
.
. By Entity, Year, Period, Seq Major, Seq Minor
.
APDISTI3DEF  INIT             "1-8,40-46,31-38,171-173"               (Index definitions for Key 2)
.
APDISTFSIZE  CONST            "190"                                   (Length of each Record)

APDISTKY    DIM               APDISTK1SIZE                            (The Actual 'Key' variable)
APDISTKY2   DIM               APDISTK2SIZE                            (The Actual 'Key' variable)
APDISTKY3   DIM               APDISTK3SIZE                            (The Actual 'Key' variable)

APDISTPROG  INIT              "Program Name"
